0.64.1 Beta review!
TL;DR: Awesome grinder, grab it! But it has no online multiplayer, only hotseat.
-------------------

Pros:
+ Will run on a potato laptop;
+ Can use WASD or mouse to move;
+ Easy to learn;
+ Nice sound and music;
+ Different skills for each characters;
+ Plenty of possible skill builds;
+ Has loot filter options;
+ Has random portals (like Vaal Areas in PoE);
+ Enchanting and crafting;
+ 100 character levels and infinite Mastery levels!

Cons:
- Gear items don't affect character visuals (yet);
- Hard to setup HUD (no real-time, game is blurred when in ESC menu);
- No online multiplayer (yet);
- Can't bind Mouse4 and 5 (GameMaker engine issue);
- Game becomes too easy (at least for archer) on max difficulty after getting a good (not best) gear.

This game has a lot of potential, totally worth buying.
